  <brief_title>Study Comparing Regional Anesthetic Blocks and Periarticular Infiltration for the Management of Post-operative Pain After Direct Anterior Total Hip Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <acronym>DA THA pain</acronym>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Study Comparing Regional Anesthetic Blocks and Periarticular Infiltration for the Management of Post-operative Pain After Direct Anterior Total Hip Replacement</official_title>
